    {
      "para_id": "Q003657.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) For Dumuzid , king of E ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q003657.3",
      "line_range": "3",
      "translation": "(i 3) Lugal-zage-si , ruler of Umma , lumah priest of Nisaba , child of Bubu , ruler of Umma , lumah priest of Nisaba , built his temple for Dumuzid , king of E , for his well-being . He drove in its foundation pegs , and put its divine powers in good order ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q003657.15",
      "line_range": "15",
      "translation": "(ii 6) He built the temple of Lisi . He built the temple of Nisaba . He built the E-ĝidru of Umma . He built the E-ĝidru of Ki'an ."
    }
  ],
